config PANICOS_DEVICE_RK3326_A
	bool "anbernic/rk3326-a (Rockchip RK3326 — legacy variant)"
	select PANICOS_SOC_ROCKCHIP_RK3326
	help
	  RK3326 devices originally shipped with hardkernel U-Boot (a-variant):
	    OGA, OGS (ODROID-GO Super), RG351M, RG351V, GameConsole R33S,
	    MagicX XU10, GameForce Chi.
	  Uses mainline U-Boot v2025.10 (which fully supports these SoCs by now)
	  with a_boot.scr for ADC-based DTB selection at runtime.

	  Kernel: Linux 6.12 LTS + ROCKNIX patches.
